<HEADLINE>
<P>
A NIGHT WITHOUT MRS. B'S 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 When I opened my TV Times one recent Saturday night, I was stunned to see that 
in place of "The Five Mrs. Buchanans" (CBS), a wonderfully funny show, was 
"Walker, Texas Ranger," which has no plot and is very violent and fake. I am 13 
and lately I have noticed that here aren't very many quality shows like "The 
Road Home," "Christy," "McKenna" and "Byrds of Paradise" on anymore. 
</P>
<P>
 Gilly Cutshaw, Fountain Valley 
</P>
