<HEADLINE>
<P>
SINGING WITH 'MATLOCK' 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Yes, we would certainly prefer watching "Matlock" (ABC) as opposed to 
"McKenna.""Matlock" is a great program and we never miss it. Good, clean and 
entertaining. We enjoy the segments where he (Andy Griffith) conducts the 
church choir and they sing the lovely hymns. 
</P>
<P>
 Dorothy and Jerry Stromberg, Reseda 
</P>
