<P>
 Regarding "The Watchdog Is on the Case," by Donald Liebenson (Dec. 4): Tim 
Lucas has some kind of nerve getting on Rhino Home Video's case because it 
released videos of horror movies with a lot of commentary by the lovely and 
talented Elvira. 
</P>
<P>
 Can't he see that the Mistress of the Dark is the main reason people buy these 
videos? As far as I'm concerned, Elvira can talk through the entire movie and 
I'd love every second of it! 
</P>
<P>
 Will this senseless Elvira-bashing ever end? 
