the headliners at the event, at the Stouffer Esmeralda and the Hyatt Grand 
Champions resorts. In addition to music and parties, dance lessons and a "Jazz 
on Film" series await. Three-day pass, $130; Dec. 30 only, $35; Dec. 31, $75; 
Jan. 1, $35. The optional New Year's Eve Jazz Buffet: $45. Hotel packages 
available. (310) 799-6055. 
