<P>
 Scrapping the atomic bomb mushroom cloud stamp by the post office was the 
right idea, but for the wrong reason. The stamp should have had two mushroom 
clouds.It took the second bombing to convince the die-hard Japanese authorities 
to surrender a week after the first one. 
</P>
