and only one of its top five scorers -- in uniform. Lindsey Hunter (broken 
ankle) and Oliver Miller (broken hand) were placed on the injured list earlier 
in the day, and Joe Dumars (bronchitis) and Grant Hill (flu) did not make the 
trip. 
</P>
