points as the New Jersey Nets took command by hitting their first 10 shots in 
winning in East Rutherford, N.J. 
</P>
<P>
 The Celtics' Dominique Wilkins was limited to nine points on four-of-21 
shooting. 
</P>
<P>
 Phoenix 103, Minnesota 89 -- Rookie Wesley Person scored seven of his 25 
points during a 17-1 run in the fourth quarter as the Suns won in Minneapolis. 
</P>
<P>
 The Suns remained perfect against Minnesota, winning all 22 meetings. 
Minnesota also extended its club-record home losing streak to 13 games, dating 
to last season. 
</P>
