<HEADLINE>
<P>
GOOD STUDENTS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 I am a high school student, and I am very pleased to hear that the students of 
Orange County are doing so well as shown on the standard tests and low dropout 
rates. 
</P>
<P>
 It is good to see that many of the students are applying themselves. 
</P>
<P>
 It is gratifying to know that teen-agers noted for irresponsibility may be 
changing some opinions. 
</P>
<P>
 O'NEIL HOPSON 
</P>
<P>
 Huntington Beach 
</P>
