<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
December 11, 1994, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 1; Column 1; National Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
