<DOCNO> LA121194-0330 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 107245 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
December 11, 1994, Sunday, Valley Edition 
</P>
