<P>
 Through an editing error in Nina Totenberg's review of "Strange Justice" and 
"Resurrection" (Nov. 13), Sen. John Danforth was misidentified as a member of 
the Senate Judiciary Committee. 
</P>
<P>
 In the same issue, the uncredited cover illustration was by Nancy Barnet. 
